query:
SELECT SUM(ISNULL(I.QTDNEG,0)) AS QTD_TOTAL_SAIDA
FROM [SANKHYA].[TGFITE] I
JOIN [SANKHYA].[TGFCAB] C ON C.NUNOTA = I.NUNOTA AND C.CODEMP = I.CODEMP
WHERE I.CODPROD = 3680
  AND C.DTNEG BETWEEN '2025-12-01' AND '2025-12-31'
  AND C.TIPMOV <> 'O'
  AND C.STATUSNOTA = 'L';
